OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FWidely fine and dry with light
OL,6,Fwinds. Feeling very warm, with the
OL,7,Fstrong July sunshine spreading to more
OL,8,Fnorthern areas as the day progresses.
OL,9,FCloud becoming confined to the far
OL,10,Fnorthwest, where still thick enough
OL,11,Ffor a little drizzle.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloud and patchy drizzle
OL,14,Fpersisting for northwest Scotland.
OL,15,FOtherwise, staying dry with prolonged
OL,16,Fclear periods. Some mist and fog
OL,17,Fpatches developing, mainly in the
OL,18,Fwest. A warm night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
