OL,5,CThursday:FEarly mist and fog soon
OL,6,Fclearing, England, Wales and eastern
OL,7,FScotland experiencing another hot day
OL,8,Fwith hazy sunshine and light winds.
OL,9,FCloudier for Northern Ireland and
OL,10,Fnorthwest Scotland.
